
# Full-Stack Todo App

A simple full-stack Todo application built to demonstrate frontend (HTML/CSS/JS) and backend (Node.js/Express) integration.

## Features
- Add, view, delete todos via intuitive UI.
- Frontend fetches/sends data to backend API.
- LocalStorage fallback for offline use.

## Setup
1. Backend: `cd backend && npm install && npm start`
2. Frontend: Open `frontend/index.html` in browser (connects to http://localhost:3000).

